sequenceDiagram
    participant App
    participant SupabaseAuth
    participant AuthProvider
    participant ItemsProvider
    participant SpeciesSync
    participant ObservabilityService
    participant UI

    App->>ObservabilityService: init(sessionId = UUID)
    App->>SupabaseAuth: Check currentSession

    alt Valid + not expired
        SupabaseAuth-->>App: Restore session
    else Expired session
        App->>SupabaseAuth: Attempt refreshSession
        alt Refresh success
            SupabaseAuth-->>App: New session tokens
        else Refresh fails
            SupabaseAuth-->>App: No valid session
            App->>UI: Navigate to LoginScreen
            Note over UI: Stop - user must authenticate
        end
    else Anonymous or no session
        App->>UI: Navigate to LoginScreen
        Note over UI: Stop - user must authenticate
    end

    App->>AuthProvider: AuthState.authenticated(UserProfile)

    Note over ItemsProvider,SpeciesSync: Parallel hydration

    par Hydrate items
        AuthProvider->>ItemsProvider: Start hydration
        ItemsProvider->>SupabaseAuth: SELECT * FROM v3_items WHERE user_id = :uid
        SupabaseAuth-->>ItemsProvider: Items data
        ItemsProvider->>ItemsProvider: Populate pack state
        ItemsProvider->>ObservabilityService: Log items.fetch_success
    and Hydrate species
        AuthProvider->>SpeciesSync: Start delta sync
        SpeciesSync->>SupabaseAuth: SELECT FROM species WHERE updated_at > :lastSync
        SupabaseAuth-->>SpeciesSync: Changed species rows
        SpeciesSync->>SpeciesSync: Update LocalSpeciesTable cache
        SpeciesSync->>ObservabilityService: Log species.sync_complete
    end

    App->>App: RecapCheck: should we show recap? (6h rule)

    alt Recap applicable
        App->>UI: Navigate to RecapScreen
        Note over UI: RecapScreen shown first, then PackScreen
    else No recap needed
        App->>UI: Navigate to PackScreen
    end
